Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1

If need not receive dri2 event, then you can add XESetWireToEvent, XESetEventToWire in EGL for emulator.

{
  DRI2QueryExtension(dpy, &ev_base, &err_base);
  DRI2QueryVersion(dpy, &major, &minor);

  if(DoNotNeedEvent)
  {
    XESetWireToEvent(dpy, ev_base+DRI2BufferSwapCompleteNotify, NULL);
    XESetWireToEvent(dpy, ev_base+DRI2InvalidateBuffersNotify, NULL);
    XESetEventToWire(dpy, ev_base+DRI2BufferSwapCompleteNotify, NULL);
    XESetEventToWire(dpy, ev_base+DRI2InvalidateBuffersNotify, NULL);
  }
}
